text: Qemal Mustafaraj (born 1 July 1995 in Fier) is an Albanian professional footballer who most recently played for Apolonia Fier in the Albanian First Division. ==Club vcareer== Mustafaraj left Apolonia in summer 2017Eksod lojtarësh nga Apolonia, nuk duan të luajnë futboll me… sufllaqe - Panorama after only joining them earlier in that year from Bylis Ballsh.Lajmi i fundit/ Apolonia nis merkaton, një mesfushor zyrtarizohet te klubi fierak - Panorama ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Fier Category:Association football forwards Category:Albanian footballers Category:KF Bylis Ballsh players Category:KF Apolonia Fier players Category:Albanian Superliga players Category:Albanian First Division players
